Comment.val: /*Program that assembles the singleOrderCancel xml message to be send to Fintegrator. */

Text.val: Virtuals to write the XML Message
Record for SingleOrderCancel not found --> Error
executingFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
clientID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
clearingFirm --> Optional, can't be filled with data
clearingAccount --> Optional, can't be filled with data
investorID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
enteringFirm --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory
settlementLocation --> Optional, can't be filled with data
originationTrader --> Optional, can't be filled with data
originationFirm --> Optional but when provided: id --> Manditory; dataSourceScheme --> Optional
securityID --> Optional, but when provided: id --> Manditory and sourceID --> Manditory
orderQtyData --> Manditory; orderQty --> Manditory OR cashOrderQty --> Manditory
